roup, New York, NY.', 'Hydrochlorothiazide, Ramipril, Valsartan, Lisinopril, Perindopril, Niacin, Acetylsalicylic acid, Ezetimibe, Bempedoic acid, Indapamide, Fenofibrate, More', 'Dacomitinib, Pexidartinib, Vemurafenib, Vandetanib, Capmatinib, Ibrutinib, Afatinib, Tivozanib, Sunitinib, Regorafenib, Alpelisib, More', 1767369485);
